metadata.name: Tripping Frog #1
metadata.description: In the land near Narnia a group of hippie frogs live near the  cabin. One day the frogs got ahold of the tabs, and the rest is history! All 696 frogs are unique and tripping ballz. They need a trip sitter! Will you be one? All nft holders have IP rights to there tripping frog! No Twitter no website no promises. Just some dope art and trippy vibez. #TrippyFrogs.
